# INI Logistics V2

A logistics management web application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## Features
- User Login
- Dashboard Analytics
- New Shipment Creation
- Shipment Management
- Shipment Tracking

## Technologies
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- GitHub Pages

## Live Demo
